Adventure Quest
===============

Introduction
------------

This is a silly roguelike game I worked on over a Christmas vacation. It
currently has no goal; just walk around and kill bats and slimes.

Controls
--------
hjkl - move (vi controls)
a    - attack
b    - buy (when at a shop)
i    - view/use inventory
d    - drop
,    - pick up
>    - go down stairs
<    - go up stairs

Z    - exit game

